<li><a href="http://www.designcouncil.org.uk/servicedesign" class="external text" title="http://www.designcouncil.org.uk/servicedesign" rel="nofollow">Design Council on Service Design</a> Design Council one stop shop information resource on Service Design by Bill Hollins.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ddc.dk/lang?l=1033&amp;u=/DESIGNVIDEN/artikler/simona_maschi_service_design/" class="external text" title="http://www.ddc.dk/lang?l=1033&amp;u=/DESIGNVIDEN/artikler/simona_maschi_service_design/" rel="nofollow">Service Design and why it matters to business</a> An interesting article / interview on service design at Danish Design Center website.</li>
<li><a href="http://nextd.org/02/09/03/index.html" class="external text" title="http://nextd.org/02/09/03/index.html" rel="nofollow">Can Service Design Save the World?</a> Gill Wildman, Chris Downs, GK VanPatter, NextDesign Leadership Institute Journal, 2006</li>
